data-processing pipelines) are licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0. A copy of the Apache 2.0 licence text is available at
https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.

You may use, modify, and redistribute the code subject to the terms
of Apache-2.0, which require attribution, retention of notices, and
do not require derivative-work disclosure.

PROSE, FIGURES, AND PAPERS
--------------------------
All prose content (Markdown documents, README files, papers, figures,
LaTeX sources where the LaTeX is not itself executable code, prose
within docstrings) is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
International (CC BY 4.0). A copy is available at
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/.

You may share and adapt this material for any purpose, including
commercially, subject to attribution.

EXTERNAL DATASETS
-----------------
External datasets referenced in this repository (OpenNeuro datasets
ds005620, ds004541, ds007609, ds004315, ds004504, ds005520, ds004505,
ds006802, ds007471, and others; BETSE planarian simulation data; ARIA
chess data; HCP cortical data) remain under their original licences.
No external dataset is redistributed in this repository unless its
licence explicitly permits redistribution.

SUMMARY
-------
Code in this repository is licensed under Apache-2.0.
Text, figures, and papers are licensed under CC BY 4.0 unless
otherwise stated.
External datasets remain under their original licences.
